  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together galangal paste, lime juice, olive oil, cumin, chili powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add chicken to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Let chicken marinate for at least 30 minutes, or up to 2 hours in the refrigerator.",
    "Remove chicken from the marinade and grill for 5-7 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, grill onion, bell pepper, zucchini, and tomato for 3-4 minutes per side, or until tender.",
    "Warm fajitas according to package instructions.",
    "Assemble fajitas by placing grilled chicken and vegetables onto the tortillas.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
